[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1052},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231004\u002F1031795777\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231004\u002F1031795777\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231004\u002F1031795777\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231004\u002F1031795777\u002F":1027,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231004\u002F1031795777\u002F":1036},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2023\u002F10\u002F04\u002Fday-20-what-is-a-discord-bot\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1012,"date":1013,"description":25,"extension":1014,"lang":1015,"meta":1016,"navigation":372,"path":1017,"readingMinutes":781,"seo":1018,"standalone":1019,"stem":1020,"tags":1021,"tldr":1024,"updated":1013,"url":1025,"__hash__":1026},"content\u002F《Node.js 不負責系列：把前端人員當作後端來用，就算是前端也能嘗試寫的後端～原來 Node.js 可以做這麼多事～》\u002FDay20-Discord-Bot？.md","Day20 - Discord Bot？","1031795777",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1003},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,44,50,53,59,62,68,71,77,83,89,92,110,113,119,122,128,138,144,155,158,164,175,178,181,233,240,255,258,263,266,282,285,294,298,301,650,657,667,670,676,683,805,812,816,819,979,990,996,999],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"Discord Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fisray_notarray_discord_bot_7ffc90d7-a1fd-4705-8a01-7c982263c868.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"除了爬蟲之外，Node.js 可以做的事情其實非常多，所以接下來將會介紹一些其他的應用的實作，也就是 Bot。",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"bot","Bot？",[12,31,32],{},"Bot 是什麼呢？我相信你應該看過不少人家說 Line Bot、Discord Bot 以及 Slack Bot，那麼這些 Bot 是什麼呢？簡單來說，Bot 就是一個自動化的程式，可以幫助你自動化一些事情，例如：自動回覆訊息、自動發送訊息、自動發送 Email 等等。",[12,34,35,36,43],{},"那我們這次要示範什麼呢？這次我打算示範一個 Discord Bot，但是在那之前我會建議你準備好一個 Discord 伺服器，並且到「",[37,38,42],"a",{"href":39,"rel":40},"https:\u002F\u002Fdiscord.com\u002Fdevelopers\u002Fdocs\u002Fintro",[41],"nofollow","Developer Portal","」建立一個機器人，如下圖點一下 Applications",[12,45,46],{},[15,47],{"alt":48,"src":49},"Applications","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_1.jpg",[12,51,52],{},"接著點一下上方的 New Application",[12,54,55],{},[15,56],{"alt":57,"src":58},"New Application","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_2.jpg",[12,60,61],{},"名稱的話，看你自己需求，我命名為「node-ithelp-2023」",[12,63,64],{},[15,65],{"alt":66,"src":67},"New Application 2","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_3.jpg",[12,69,70],{},"新增完畢後，找到你剛剛新增的 Application，然後點一下左邊的 Bot，接著你可以找到「Reset Token」按鈕，點一下就可以取得 Token",[12,72,73],{},[15,74],{"alt":75,"src":76},"Get Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_4.jpg",[12,78,79],{},[80,81,82],"strong",{},"請注意這個 Token 不要外流，稍後我們練習會使用到。",[12,84,85],{},[15,86],{"alt":87,"src":88},"Token 很重要","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002F1694789575685.png",[12,90,91],{},"Token 大概會長這樣（底下不用擔心，我已經把 Token 換掉了）：",[93,94,99],"pre",{"className":95,"code":96,"language":97,"meta":98,"style":98},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","MTE0ODExxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx.GJ6bFp.t1h86ISWswdqidu173ydwmawd1213P9mNj9qbXlhI\n","bash","",[100,101,102],"code",{"__ignoreMap":98},[103,104,107],"span",{"class":105,"line":106},"line",1,[103,108,96],{"class":109},"smYoP",[12,111,112],{},"接下來，我們可能有些操作會需要一些權限，所以麻煩往下滾到「Privileged Gateway Intents」，這個區塊主要是操作權限，底下要請你把底下的權限都打開，如下圖：",[12,114,115],{},[15,116],{"alt":117,"src":118},"Privileged Gateway Intents","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_5.jpg",[12,120,121],{},"最後我們就是要把這個 Bot 加入到我們的伺服器，所以點一下「OAuth2」取得 Client ID",[12,123,124],{},[15,125],{"alt":126,"src":127},"Client ID","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_client_id.jpg",[12,129,130,131,133,134,137],{},"取得後接著點「Url Generator」，並勾選 ",[100,132,28],{}," 與 ",[100,135,136],{},"Administrator","，如下圖：",[12,139,140],{},[15,141],{"alt":142,"src":143},"Discord Url","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_6.jpg",[145,146,149],"callout",{"title":147,"type":148},"Note","note",[12,150,151,152,154],{},"為了方便練習才選 ",[80,153,136],{},"，實際開發上還是會依照 Bot 的需求來設定權限。",[12,156,157],{},"最後你往下滾就可以看到邀請連結了，複製下來貼上到瀏覽器，然後選擇你要加入的伺服器就搞定囉！",[12,159,160],{},[15,161],{"alt":162,"src":163},"Discord Url 2","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fdiscord_bot_url.jpg",[145,165,166],{"title":147,"type":148},[12,167,168,169,174],{},"Discord 是一款遊戲社群軟體（許多技術社群也都陸續轉移到此軟體），你可以在上面建立一個伺服器，然後邀請你的朋友一起加入，然後你們就可以在上面聊天、玩遊戲等等，如果你有興趣的話，可以參考我這一篇文章「",[37,170,173],{"href":171,"rel":172},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20220428\u002F1571298383\u002F",[41],"Discord 好難？不怕！我教你！","」。",[20,176,177],{"id":177},"專案環境",[12,179,180],{},"首先我們先來建立一個專案",[93,182,184],{"className":95,"code":183,"language":97,"meta":98,"style":98},"mkdir discord-bot-example\ncd discord-bot-example\nnpm init -y\ntouch index.js\ntouch register.js\n",[100,185,186,195,204,216,225],{"__ignoreMap":98},[103,187,188,191],{"class":105,"line":106},[103,189,190],{"class":109},"mkdir",[103,192,194],{"class":193},"sWayO"," discord-bot-example\n",[103,196,198,202],{"class":105,"line":197},2,[103,199,201],{"class":200},"stw71","cd",[103,203,194],{"class":193},[103,205,207,210,213],{"class":105,"line":206},3,[103,208,209],{"class":109},"npm",[103,211,212],{"class":193}," init",[103,214,215],{"class":200}," -y\n",[103,217,219,222],{"class":105,"line":218},4,[103,220,221],{"class":109},"touch",[103,223,224],{"class":193}," index.js\n",[103,226,228,230],{"class":105,"line":227},5,[103,229,221],{"class":109},[103,231,232],{"class":193}," register.js\n",[12,234,235,236,239],{},"接下來我們要來安裝 ",[100,237,238],{},"discord.js"," 套件，這個套件是用來實作 Discord Bot 的，所以我們必須要安裝這個套件",[93,241,243],{"className":95,"code":242,"language":97,"meta":98,"style":98},"npm i discord.js\n",[100,244,245],{"__ignoreMap":98},[103,246,247,249,252],{"class":105,"line":106},[103,248,209],{"class":109},[103,250,251],{"class":193}," i",[103,253,254],{"class":193}," discord.js\n",[12,256,257],{},"這是由 Discord 官方所提供的套件，所以你可以放心的使用。",[145,259,260],{"title":147,"type":148},[12,261,262],{},"如果你熟悉其他語言的話，也可以嘗試使用 Python、Go 等套件唷！",[12,264,265],{},"這邊有件事情我要特別提醒一下，由於接下來的實作我們要使用比較新版的 Discord Bot，所以建議你切換到 Node.js 18 會比較好唷！",[93,267,269],{"className":95,"code":268,"language":97,"meta":98,"style":98},"nvm use 18\n",[100,270,271],{"__ignoreMap":98},[103,272,273,276,279],{"class":105,"line":106},[103,274,275],{"class":109},"nvm",[103,277,278],{"class":193}," use",[103,280,281],{"class":200}," 18\n",[20,283,284],{"id":284},"實作",[12,286,287,288,293],{},"接下來我們會來實作一個簡易的 Discord Bot，那麼該怎麼起手呢？其實",[37,289,292],{"href":290,"rel":291},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.npmjs.com\u002Fpackage\u002Fdiscord.js",[41],"官方文件","都有提供範例程式碼，但官方程式碼是基於 ES6 的語法，所以底下我還是會介紹一下。",[295,296,297],"h3",{"id":297},"註冊指令",[12,299,300],{},"首先我們來看第一個範例，也就是註冊指令，不用擔心，這邊我會逐行補上註解說明：",[93,302,306],{"className":303,"code":304,"language":305,"meta":98,"style":98},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","\u002F\u002F register.js\nconst {\n  REST, \u002F\u002F 引入 REST\n  Routes \u002F\u002F 引入 Routes\n} = require('discord.js'); \u002F\u002F 引入 discord.js 套件\n\n\u002F\u002F 指令表\nconst list = [\n  {\n    name: 'ping', \u002F\u002F 指令名稱\n    description: 'Replies with Pong!', \u002F\u002F 指令描述\n  },\n];\n\n\u002F\u002F 實例化 REST，並設定版本與 Token\nconst rest = new REST({ version: '10' }).setToken(TOKEN);\n\nconst registerCommands = async (commands) => {\n  try {\n    console.log('Started refreshing application (\u002F) commands.');\n    \u002F\u002F 註冊指令\n    await rest.put(Routes.applicationCommands(CLIENT_ID), { body: commands });\n\n    console.log('Successfully reloaded application (\u002F) commands.');\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error(error);\n  }\n}\n\n\u002F\u002F 執行註冊指令\nregisterCommands(list);\n","js",[100,307,308,314,324,335,343,367,374,380,394,400,414,428,434,440,445,451,487,492,520,528,544,550,576,581,595,607,618,624,630,635,641],{"__ignoreMap":98},[103,309,310],{"class":105,"line":106},[103,311,313],{"class":312},"sGBqm","\u002F\u002F register.js\n",[103,315,316,320],{"class":105,"line":197},[103,317,319],{"class":318},"sOudu","const",[103,321,323],{"class":322},"s8XSl"," {\n",[103,325,326,329,332],{"class":105,"line":206},[103,327,328],{"class":200},"  REST",[103,330,331],{"class":322},", ",[103,333,334],{"class":312},"\u002F\u002F 引入 REST\n",[103,336,337,340],{"class":105,"line":218},[103,338,339],{"class":200},"  Routes",[103,341,342],{"class":312}," \u002F\u002F 引入 Routes\n",[103,344,345,348,351,355,358,361,364],{"class":105,"line":227},[103,346,347],{"class":322},"} ",[103,349,350],{"class":318},"=",[103,352,354],{"class":353},"scAaK"," require",[103,356,357],{"class":322},"(",[103,359,360],{"class":193},"'discord.js'",[103,362,363],{"class":322},"); ",[103,365,366],{"class":312},"\u002F\u002F 引入 discord.js 套件\n",[103,368,370],{"class":105,"line":369},6,[103,371,373],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":372},true,"\n",[103,375,377],{"class":105,"line":376},7,[103,378,379],{"class":312},"\u002F\u002F 指令表\n",[103,381,383,385,388,391],{"class":105,"line":382},8,[103,384,319],{"class":318},[103,386,387],{"class":200}," list",[103,389,390],{"class":318}," =",[103,392,393],{"class":322}," [\n",[103,395,397],{"class":105,"line":396},9,[103,398,399],{"class":322},"  {\n",[103,401,403,406,409,411],{"class":105,"line":402},10,[103,404,405],{"class":322},"    name: ",[103,407,408],{"class":193},"'ping'",[103,410,331],{"class":322},[103,412,413],{"class":312},"\u002F\u002F 指令名稱\n",[103,415,417,420,423,425],{"class":105,"line":416},11,[103,418,419],{"class":322},"    description: ",[103,421,422]